::Shadow Stalker::

As Shadow Stalker walks out of the CR Chamber he decided it would be best if 
joins the maximals, but first he'd have to find a maximal.  So he spoke into 
his comm-link,"Hey Rex I'd like to see you for a moment, this concerns 
joining the maximals."  Now Shadow Stalker is waiting for a response or for 
another maximal to accept him somewhere around the area.
